Intel Science & Technology Center for Embedded Computing
AndyVision / Project Agora / Future of Retail
08/15/12

This is a ROS-based, distributed software environment for the Agora robot -- specifically,
predicated on the ELECTRIC version of ROS. Setup and tutorial information is included 
below.

- install ROS electric -- http://www.ros.org/wiki/electric/Installation
- acquaint yourself with the ROS environment -- http://www.ros.org/wiki/ROS/Tutorials

- contact Jon for repository access -- jmfrancis@cmu.edu
- clone agora robot development repository -- git clone https://USERNAME@bitbucket.org/USERNAME/agorarobot.git

- add "source ~/agorarobot/ros/setup.bash" to ~/.bashrc
- add "source /opt/ros/electric/setup.sh" to the end of "~/.bashrc"
- add ":~/agorarobot/ros" to the end of ROS_PACKAGE_PATH in {ROS_ROOT}/setup.sh

- contact Jon if you have any questions
